{"tid":87162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]深圳婆媳糾紛釀命案　六旬家姑殺媳婦後墮亡","createTime":"2017-01-19T14:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T15:01:30.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41a178688b3a635f4409b53485b3ebf8b717e023","tid":87162,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/bkncn-20170119193152809-0119_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170119%2Fbkncn-20170119193152809-0119_05011_001.html&d=hOZCSuynYZfFE9uXVR4tkXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=15ae0f6d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/bkncn-20170119193152809-0119_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n深圳寶安新安街道一個屋苑昨日發生倫常命案，61歲婦人裴X菊疑因家庭糾紛，持鈍器襲擊30歲李姓媳婦致死後，跳樓自殺當場身亡。警方接報趕抵現場處置，案件詳情有待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n附近一名商舖老闆表示，昨日上午8時許，他正在店裏工作時，突然聽到外面傳來一聲巨響，「以為是撞車了」，走到門外才赫見一人躺在地上。警方到場拉起封鎖線，多人在旁圍觀。事發後，現場還留有血漬。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒指，裴X菊一家住在12樓的單位，事發後，大廈的升降機及12樓地面都用水清洗過。但從12樓步向上的樓梯間，仍可隱約看到多個血腳印。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3971b93aeee1872b631556157d5e489ea50a54","tid":87162,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"001f7fed72b7fee435b789d1b2f09164f4d94ebb","tid":87162,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}